body_html:
@asimshankar

From 30,000' our program does these three things:

  1. Read in existing TensorFlow network file
  2. Correlate our gpuDetails business data with each node in the network
  3. Write out TensorBoard event file.

The user does not get access to or manipulate GpuDetails protobuf.
Instead, our program is injecting our gpuDetails data into each node on an existing graph.
